install ejs from npm
npm i ejs
app.set("view engine", "ejs");
create a views folder
create a view index.ejs
load the html in the  place of the res.send to render any page from views folder


from jab bhi  submit karoge pahli cheej ye dekhiye ki saari fiels ke pass name property hai ya nahi
from ke pass action hai ya nahibackend ke pass route hai ya nahi
backend ke pass route hai ya nahi
wo route ka type sahi hai ya nahi
route ke ander aapka data unke type ke hisaab se milega
     GET - req.query
     POST - req.body


post data ko samajhne ke liye 